data.description: This cozy conventional is just waiting for a new owner!  Many updates in the last few years, including the garage roof in 2020.  The furnace was replaced the same year, allowing for years of worry free temperature control in the colder months.  The dishwasher was replaced in 2020, and both it and the stove will stay with the home.  The electric was updated in 2020, and the toilet and vanity were also replaced that year.  There is one regular bedroom and also a Jack & Jill bedroom that can be used as 2 separate bedrooms, so the house has as many as 3 bedrooms if need be.  All of this and at a great price, too!  Come check out 363 Columbia St today.
